{
  "stem": "25809.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, bit by bit, we brought it, actually, over before we went into hiding, come to think of it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We would come back again and then take some more clothing with us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we couldn't take [LAUGHS] a suitcase or a-- or a big sack.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yeah, we could maybe take a shopping bag, you know, like we had gone shopping.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that was about [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the most we could do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had no toys as a kid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't have too many toys, but I had no toys.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only thing I had was maybe some paper and-- to write on, with a pencil.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And even that was limited.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Didn't-- I had literally nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I would sit there in what you might call our underground place, and kind of look out of the window, make sure that nobody could see me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I would look through the-- the curtains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And just do nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had a radio and I would listen to the radio.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we would listen to Hitler when he would speak, which of course was not encouraging, because his speeches were-- you know, as much as I could understand from it-- were not encouraging to listen to at all.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But anyhow, my-- when we moved in there, we moved-- we moved into hiding-- my father, my mother, my sister, and I were there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And a few months later, things got-- I had a-- had a grandmother, an aunt, her daughter, and an uncle, and they were staying-- had an-- another uncle of mine who was married to a Christian lady.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And therefore, the mixed marriage was not subject to the Nazi persecution.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were staying there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But it was getting too dangerous for them to stay there.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
